definitions.definition: A man who drives a horse-drawn coach , a male coach driver .
A fish in the genus Heniochus , either Heniochus acuminatus or Heniochus diphreutes .

main_definition: A man who drives a horse-drawn coach , a male coach driver .
secondary_definitions: ( South Africa ) A fish in the genus Heniochus , either Heniochus acuminatus or Heniochus diphreutes .
